data.title: WO2019224092A1 - Pesticidally active c15-derivatives of ginkgolides - Google Patents
data.meta_description: The invention relates to the use of ginkgolide derivatives of formula (I), wherein the variables are defined in the specification; as agrochemical pesticide. It also relates to certain comppounds of formula (I); to mixtures, agrochemical and veterinary compositions, and seed containing the compounds, and to methods of application for combating pests.
